These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, pink
2 different games are played: scrabble, canasta
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, pilot
1. the pilot is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes pink is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the pilot is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Color   | pink     | purple   |
| Game         | canasta | scrabble |
| Job     | analyst | pilot    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different games are played: scrabble, bridge
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, daisy
1. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Game          | scrabble     | bridge |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Beverage           | sprite         | cola     |
| Flower     | iris   | daisy    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, lavender
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, spy
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
City: nizza, prague
1. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person who likes coral is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Color    | lavender     | coral |
| Movie-Genre         | spy | action    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| City   | nizza         | prague    |

 #################################

 
