.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
City: venice, prague
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, havana
House: colonial, futuristic
1. the futuristic house is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to prague is the dutch##1
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| City           | prague | venice    |
| Nationality   | dutch       | egyptian |
| Cigar           | vegafina         | havana    |
| House         | colonial    | futuristic   |

