.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, davidoff
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, action
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, dubstep
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Cigar         | davidoff        | chaman |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure          | action     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel        | dubstep     |

 